cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning multilingual word embeddings and crosslingual semantic similarity tasks.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the proposed method involves using image-text data to learn multilingual embeddings.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for learning embeddings using weakly-supervised data.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with semantic similarity tasks.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the proposed method involves using both image and text data.
